{"tid":1805821,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"維園民陣遊行最後一推","createTime":"2020-01-01T00:43:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-01T05:00:26.000Z","uid":318282,"like":10,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"6a143cee2ebd08330569fcde3c3fba84420d3549","tid":1805821,"uid":318282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T00:43:00.000Z","msg":"各位手足即使琴日玩到好夜<br />\n可能真係會好攰 但係琴日有好多人冇得玩<br />\n今日有不反 出黎一定要提早一個鐘出盡量唔好遲<br />\n一定要行維園入 呢個係大家一定要做嘅<br />\n要你地等下咋 唔係要你地上前擋子彈<br />\n2020年有好多位手足同唔倒我地過<br />\n但佢地會守護住2019年嘅香港<br />\n你地會唔會幫佢地行呢個遊行？<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vmxWPaf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvmxWPaf.jpg&h=99877335&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n光復香港唔係淨係得講<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81ca45f13477d2c0ad3a38f461da9f3fe0db4994","tid":1805821,"uid":228319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T00:43:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6dcd3c374fa1ea56623ac6cb4f67e51efa3c80ba","tid":1805821,"uid":57322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T01:04:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e264faa06ad359c87f17377d3e6f75413ccd6ee0","tid":1805821,"uid":299639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T02:01:39.000Z","msg":"維園見"},{"pid":"770d333090f09fc640d9b4a7bafc4749140f697c","tid":1805821,"uid":187489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T04:50:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3ec4f4b53f28b26303db7e3186ef6e40a60b5a2c","tid":1805821,"uid":69841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T04:51:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ADV9aSP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FADV9aSP.png&h=291c3a32&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9f209aa1cad05831500030bcdbf3ddbd3266cbea","tid":1805821,"uid":69334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T04:51:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/beg_c